y.\", \"from\": 350, \"to\": 517, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 350, \"end\": 354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.7868281853159214, \"rank\": 0.270333529319969, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 370, \"end\": 380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9999737923302309, \"rank\": 1.4221279643820261e-05, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"B-Girl Raygun\", \"from\": 422, \"to\": 435}, {\"ngram\": \"her round robin battles\", \"from\": 455, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"a combined score\", \"from\": 482, \"to\": 498}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 516}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I love Rachael, and I think that what has occurred on social media with trolls and keyboard warriors, and taking those comments and giving them air time, has been really disappointing,\\\" Meares told a news conference on Saturday.\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 748, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 527, \"end\": 534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"score\": 0.999999990873448, \"rank\": 4.661035668712041e-09, \"text\": \"Rachael\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 574, \"to\": 586}, {\"ngram\": \"trolls\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 598}, {\"ngram\": \"keyboard warriors\", \"from\": 603, \"to\": 620}, {\"ngram\": \"those comments\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 647}, {\"ngram\": \"air time\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 672}, {\"ngram\": \"Meares\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 712}, {\"ngram\": \"a news conference\", \"from\": 718, \"to\": 735}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 747}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Raygun is an absolutely loved member of this Olympic team.\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 809, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Raygun\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 757}, {\"ngram\": \"an absolutely loved member\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 787}, {\"ngram\": \"this Olympic team\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 808}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has represented the Olympic team, the Olympic spirit with great enthusiasm.\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 889, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic team\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 846}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic spirit\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 866}, {\"ngram\": \"great enthusiasm\", \"from\": 872, \"to\": 888}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I absolutely love her courage.\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 926, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her courage\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 925}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I love her character, and I feel very disappointed for her, that she has come under the attack that she has.\\\"\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 1036, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her character\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 947}, {\"ngram\": \"the attack\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1021}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meares said that criticism of Gunn's performance and appearance was consistent with the sort of misogynistic abuse that female athletes had suffered over the last century as they fought for their space in the sporting world.\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1262, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1068, \"end\": 1072, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.7868281853159214, \"rank\": 0.270333529319969, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Meares\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1044}, {\"ngram\": \"criticism\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1064}, {\"ngram\": \"appearance\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1101}, {\"ngram\